title: Monty Lopez tells us what it‘s like being Addison Rae‘s dad!
description:
Monty Lopez is the father of Addison Rae. He comes on the pod to tell us whats going on in his life. We talk about how Addison Rae blew up, and so much more! Like, Subscribe, and comment!
